## üß∞ Materials List  

| Material                  | Description                                 |
|---------------------------|---------------------------------------------|
| Fungal spawn              | *Pleurotus*, *Ganoderma*, or local mycelium |
| Frame material            | Bamboo, PVC, steel, or salvaged tubing      |
| Outer shell               | Burlap, breathable canvas, or bioplastic     |
| Fill layer                | Biochar, activated carbon, straw            |
| Watering system           | Drip line or solar fog collector            |
| Mesh inlets               | Stainless mesh or recycled filters          |
| Solar vent (optional)     | 5W solar fan for assisted convection        |

